methods.and:

*Overload 2*

  :return: (java.lang.Boolean) logical and of all the values in the array.

Returns the nth value from an array.

*Overload 1*

  :param values: (io.deephaven.vector.BooleanVector) - values.

*Overload 2*

methods.nullToValue:
Replaces null values with a default value.

*Overload 1*  
  :param value: (java.lang.Boolean) - value.
  :param defaultValue: (boolean) - default value to return for null values.
  :return: (java.lang.Boolean) value, if value is not null, and defaultValue if value is null.
  
*Overload 2*  
  :param values: (io.deephaven.vector.BooleanVector) - values.
  :param defaultValue: (boolean) - default value to return for null values.
  :return: (java.lang.Boolean[]) value, if value is not null, and defaultValue if value is null.

methods.sum:
**Incompatible overloads text - text from the first overload:**

Returns the sum of the values in an array.  For booleans, this is equivalent to "or".

*Overload 1*  
  :param values: (java.lang.Boolean...) - values.
  :return: (java.lang.Boolean) sum of the values.  This is equivalent to "or".
  
*Overload 2*
